{"tid":2261038,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"控方見開機慢兩小時 質疑拍片紀錄不準  辯方：手機無SIM卡時間會錯","createTime":"2020-10-28T04:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T04:49:06.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d55427a91b22604aab8423bdd9fafc0d83621f6","tid":2261038,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:45:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/J5OLVR3OCRA3HAHGMK5FOX5A6A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FJ5OLVR3OCRA3HAHGMK5FOX5A6A%2F&d=wqADD7%2BrbugmZDmBsEVo7A2E5jpmEl9YQHmcT4noKO0%3D&h=abc022e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FJ5OLVR3OCRA3HAHGMK5FOX5A6A%2F&h=5e4d5664\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/J5OLVR3OCRA3HAHGMK5FOX5A6A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n控方見開機慢兩小時 質疑拍片紀錄不準 <br />\n辯方：手機無SIM卡時間會錯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/b-almAA5Okdh2LhnJLmFP1qdk6M=/720x482/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X7ZX3SSEGZAU7LZO6PL26RQOY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fb-almAA5Okdh2LhnJLmFP1qdk6M%3D%2F720x482%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX7ZX3SSEGZAU7LZO6PL26RQOY4.jpg&h=4743b524&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告鄧楚豐的手機昨被控方指時間不準。<br />\n<br />\n【堵路案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年11月大三罷行動期間，有男生被指和其他示威者在筲箕灣道一帶堵路，警員昨力證遠距離目擊揹着黑色背囊的被告在案發地點丟低石頭，但無論口供紙和記事冊內均無提及黑色背囊。被告則堅稱被捕前一直在天橋上用手機拍攝，沒有參與，辯方在庭上播放相關手機影片，冀證明被告當時不在筲箕灣道，遭控方質疑手機上的時間比正確時間慢兩小時，準確性存疑，但原來手機自被告被捕後一直遭警方扣查及無SIM卡，時間停留在11月，直至昨日才開機。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。在筲箕灣道與成安街交界，非法以磚頭和垃圾阻礙交通。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3hCokAW0tUmIsGojbVaLUBVcx1k=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IM6UK5RAFNCCHHKXVFUDEMAHSI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3hCokAW0tUmIsGojbVaLUBVcx1k%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIM6UK5RAFNCCHHKXVFUDEMAHSI.jpg&h=46ed3ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年11月13日全港大三罷，多區有人堵路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警認口供「寫得唔好」<br />\n<br />\n警員溫偉樂昨供稱，看見40至50名示威者逃走，遠距離見揹着黑色背囊的被告丟下石頭，迎面跑來，於是截停被告，其背囊上有彩色圖案。警員稱當時認為只記下被告身穿黑衣已足夠，故無論口供紙和記事冊內均無提及黑色背囊。辯方質疑「當時個個都着黑衫，黑色有圖案的背囊唔係特殊特徵？」警員僅稱「自己寫得唔好」。至於為何口供紙寫是30至40人，溫稱剛才「口誤」，人數應是30至40人。<br />\n<br />\n被告表面證供成立，他出庭自辯稱，當日學校因示威活動宣佈停課，於是回家，在手機上見到西灣河堵路活動的新聞，因好奇前往視察。出門前他穿上黑衫灰褲，又戴上黑色口罩，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方播片，拍攝時間為早上11時44分，被告則於五分鐘後被捕。辯方認為影片足以證明被告被捕前五分鐘在天橋上，而非在筲箕灣道設路障。<br />\n<br />\n控方質疑，手機上的時間比正確時間慢兩小時，無從確認當日手機的時間是否準確。辯方更正，被告手機的時間是遲了一年，而非兩小時，指手機自被告後遭警方扣查，已關機近一年，機內無SIM卡，此情況實屬正常。裁判官黃雅茵押後至下月3日裁決。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC789/20"},{"pid":"99d5be97f84e2e2bc3d1c345f4465a452d1a7057","tid":2261038,"uid":126731,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:49:01.000Z","msg":"條片time stamp 點會錯，又生豬肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd7ea667fd385be5e577ff49298d8f39c6d37fd6","tid":2261038,"uid":65858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:49:06.000Z","msg":"律政司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}